summary: I'm gonna trust you all to use this responsibly.
descriptionHtml:
Just an asian-ish female preset that I kind of didn't want to release, but did anyway since there aren't many asian female presets around.

No, I'm not going to make an ECE version.

[b][color=#ff0000][size=4]Installation: [/size][/color][/b]

Extract the contents of the archive to your CharGen folder.

Switch to a human race if you're not already using one. I used BRETON for this. Also compatible with The Uchiha Clan.  
This file comes with both the presets, prefixed with GIVE, and the head sculpts, which you can load in the sculpt section of Racemenu.



[color=#ff0000][size=4][b]Required:[/b][/size][/color] 

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu 3.2+[/url], obviously. 
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]SG Eyebrows[/url]
SG Hairs 268 (Find it yourself)
[url=http://skyrimshot.blog.fc2.com/blog-entry-79.html]Salahair[/url]

[b][color=#ff0000][size=4]Not required, but highly recommended to be used with this, since I used them to make these:
[/size][/color][/b][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG Female Textures[/url]
[url=https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/0B10mYnxNt_bQT0lPWUJRc2xhVWc]Asianized SG Female Textures[/url] (Facial normal maps)

[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51136/?]The Uchiha Clan
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50032/?]KJ Tattoos[/url]

[b][color=#ff0000][size=4][u]Permissions:
[/u][/size][/color][/b]Do not make a follower out of this preset. I will when I have the time.
I'm gonna trust you all to use this responsibly. Don't make me regret this...
